               <div class="span12" id="narrow-content">
        
                <h1>InPost Launches Virtual Address Service Just in Time for Holiday Shopping Rush <span class="subtitle">10/26/2016</span> </h1>
                                                                        <div class="row">
                        <div class="span12 module-676 " id="" >
                                    <div class="prose" itemprop="articleBody">
<div>
<p><a href="https://va.inpost24.ca" target="_blank"> <img border="0" alt="va.inpost24.ca" src="http://images.inpost24.ca/website/VA_Fade.png" width="937" height="388" /> </a></p>
</div>
<div>
<p>Try it for Free at <a href="https://va.inpost24.ca" target="_blank">va.inpost24.ca</a>!</p>
</div>
<div>
<p>It&rsquo;s finally here! The InPost team is proud to announce that our Virtual Address service is live! Now everyone can have their e-commerce deliveries sent to their favourite InPost 24/7 Locker.</p>
<div>
<div>
<p>The service is incredibly simple to use. Just set up an account and select the InPost Locker where you would like to receive your deliveries and we&rsquo;ll provide you with your very own Virtual Address. From then on you can use your Virtual Address in place of your shipping address for deliveries and we&rsquo;ll receive the parcel on your behalf and deliver it to the InPost Locker of your choice. As soon as the item arrives in the locker you will be notified via email and text message that your delivery is waiting for you with pickup available 24 hours a day 7 days a week!</p>
<div>
<div>
<p>What it means is that you finally can take control of all your parcel deliveries from any e-commerce retailer, just in time for the holidays. At InPost it&rsquo;s our mission to empower e-commerce shoppers to have full control over their own time, letting the parcel wait for them at any one of our hundreds of convenient locations across the Greater Toronto Area (and soon to be across the whole country).</p>
<div>
<div>
<p>So join the revolution, try us for Free, the first parcel is on us!</p>
<div>
<div>
<p>The InPost parcel-locker network is the largest international network of automated parcel lockers making it easy to send and receive parcels 24/7.&nbsp; They are located in convenient places such as grocery stores, gas station and transit hubs. This customized solution is already present in more than a dozen countries, including:&nbsp; Australia, Chile, Columbia, Czech Republic, Estonia, France, Great Britain, Ireland, Iceland, Italy, Latvia, Lithuania, Poland, Russia and Slovakia. Currently, there are more than 4,500 parcel lockers based on InPost technology located worldwide.</p>
<div></div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
